{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC05_KEI_690.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x3a,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, Keith, I believe I told you that this facility is closed."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I'm sorry, but I just need to know."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I know I'm being selfish, but please tell me about the two cradles!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I would like to give you the information you need, Ayesha..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x117,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "However, disclosing confidential information violates Article 271 of the Confidentiality Order."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x118,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I find it difficult to make sound judgments... What should I do, Master...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Master...? Do you mean the person who created you, and gave you your orders?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Then he's probably also the one who ordered her to maintain the confidentiality of the information..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x118,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yes. That was the last order given to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x118,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "It's been...a long time since then."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "How unfortunate. You still hold fast to orders from nearly a thousand years ago..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x118,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "For us to continue functioning normally, we have no choice but to faithfully follow the orders that were given to us."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x118,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "If we do not, we would lose our purpose for existing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I guess you can't overturn the order... Then how about I give you a new order?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x119,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Does that mean you will become my new master?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "That's right. And, I will give you new orders to overwrite your old ones. Then there shouldn't be any problem, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x91,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Or do you not like the idea of having me as your master?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x198,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "...No. Possessing extensive knowledge in every field, you are a suitable person to be my master."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "If you became Master, I would..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x92,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Well, I'm honored. Then...I shall be your new master."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x185,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Understood. I acknowledge Keithgriff Hazeldine as my master, and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x186,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I transfer this library and all managerial authority that I possess to him."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x95,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I order you, as your master..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x97,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "To disclose all information regarding the two cradles!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x186,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Understood. In obedience to Master's<CR>order, disclosing Secret Matter<CR>No. 527..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Ms. Odelia..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x186,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "The cradles are the mediums which were established as protection mechanisms to deal with unexpected incidents."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x186,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "This library counts as one of them. A cradle to protect and to provide various knowledge...that is the Zweiteturm."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x186,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "The keeper, Odelia, was created as<CR>the guardian to protect the cradle<CR>of intellect. "
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "So, this is the cradle that protects knowledge..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Though, she's a bit unreliable as a guardian. Various places in here are full of deficiencies..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x187,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Due to unforeseen circumstances, serious incidents have occurred in this facility, bringing about disorder."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Please accept my apologies for my shortcomings."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Ms. Odelia, then the other cradle is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "The other cradle...is to protect and to provide various seeds."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "To protect life from the destruction<CR>to come, preserving the next<CR>generation...that is the Dritteturm."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Guardian Yggdrasil, who presides over the cradle of life, was also created around the same time as I was."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "He protects life, and I protect knowledge."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "...That is all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "The guardian of the cradle that protects life. That's who took Nio away...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "I keep and store various knowledge. It can be assumed that he does the same with living beings."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "I went to every means to withstand a crisis."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x117,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "He, too, probably tried all possible means...though this is merely speculation."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x118,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "With no record of him after the disaster, what happened to him..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x118,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "And also what happened to the cradle that he protected is not known to this day."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "msg_string": "So, his goal of taking away your sister was to preserve the seed..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2e,
            "msg_string": "Then Nio is being \"protected\" by him?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2f,
            "msg_string": "If he is functioning as he should be. Superficially, it looks like he's gone out of control, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x119,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x30,
            "msg_string": "Master, I have disclosed all information regarding the cradles."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x31,
            "msg_string": "Can I lift the closing of this facility, and switch back to normal operations?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x32,
            "msg_string": "Yes, do that. Closing this place down is preposterous."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x198,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x33,
            "msg_string": "Understood. Then I will start the reopening preparations."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x34,
            "msg_string": "The facility has reverted to normal operations. Please let me know if you need anything."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x35,
            "msg_string": "Thank you very much, Ms. Odelia...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x36,
            "msg_string": "The being that took Nio away has been identified, but we still don't know its location..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x0,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x37,
            "msg_string": "Right, we need to look for the cradle's location."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x38,
            "msg_string": "I'm gonna go search for it right away. Thank you so much!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x39,
            "msg_string": "However, if my assumption is correct, the being that will confront us may not be malicious, but..."
        }
    ]
}